          placeholder-ghDark-light text-white text-sm font-brand font-regular " 
        placeholder="Search..."
      />
      <button class="mt-2 mr-2 text-white text-[1rem] font-brand font-bold hover:text-ghDark-light">All gists</button>
    </div>
  </div>

</header>
